<p>The University of Sheffield Chemistry Researchers Society, is a new group open to all researchers (postdocs, fellows, technical staff and post grads wanting to stay in research) that work in the department of chemistry. </p>
<p>CRS aims to provide:</p>
<ul>
<li> Opportunities for career and personal development </li>
<li> A medium for networking, resource sharing and socialising </li>
<li> Act as a collective voice for researchers with in the department </li>
</ul>  


